headline: Here Are Friday’s Top Wall Street Analyst Research Calls: Applied Materials, Caterpillar, Home Depot, Microsoft, Shake Shack, StubHub and More
summary: Pre-Market Stock Futures: The futures are trading lower to close out the week after a dreadful day on Wall Street on Thursday, during which all the major indices were hammered. Once again, as has been the case most of this week, the NASDAQ took the heaviest brunt of the selling, closing down an incredible 2.30% ...
